title: IAA Tonight | Dallas' Options with Dak Out
description: Dak Prescott suffered a thumb injury in the Cowboys season opener, which will keep him out for some time. What options do the Cowboys have at QB to fill in while Dak recovers? Should they pursue a trade for Teddy Bridgewater or Jimmy Garoppolo? Plus, are the Packers in trouble after their abysmal showing week 1 without Davante Adams?
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Omar Kelly, Adam Pacman Jones)
